('nba-ecf-2026-g1','NBA','nba-ecf-2026','East CF',1,'2026-05-20','New York Knicks','Cleveland Cavaliers',115,104,'Madison Square Garden, New York NY','resolveBundle:NBA_ESPN','Brunson 38 pts. Knicks erased a 22-point Q4 deficit to win in OT. Sam Merrill nearly hit the buzzer-beater. NYK leads series 1-0.','NYK wins 115-104',NULL,NULL,'NBA Playoffs – East CF G1 · NYK wins 115-104',NULL),
