('nba-wcf-2026-g3','NBA','nba-wcf-2026','West CF',3,'2026-05-23','San Antonio Spurs','Oklahoma City Thunder',108,123,'Frost Bank Center, San Antonio TX','resolveBundle:NBA_NBC','OKC wins G3 123-108 (Gilgeous-Alexander 36pts). SAS won G4 103-82 (Wembanyama 33pts). Series tied 2-2. G5 Tuesday at OKC.','OKC leads 2-1','9,9,15,-1,-1,-1,-1',NULL,'NBA Playoffs – West CF G3 · OKC wins 123-108',NULL),
('nba-wcf-2026-g4','NBA','nba-wcf-2026','West CF',4,'2026-05-25','San Antonio Spurs','Oklahoma City Thunder',103,82,'Frost Bank Center, San Antonio TX','resolveBundle:NBA_NBC','SAS evens series with dominant 103-82 G4 win. Wembanyama 33pts/8reb/5ast/3blk. SGA held to 19pts (6-15 FG). OKC shot 33% FG, 18% from 3. Series returns to Paycom Center for G5 Tuesday.','Series tied 2-2','9,9,15,-21,-1,-1,-1',NULL,'NBA Playoffs – West CF G4 · SAS wins 103-82, series tied 2-2',NULL),
('nba-wcf-2026-g5','NBA','nba-wcf-2026','West CF',5,'2026-05-27','Oklahoma City Thunder','San Antonio Spurs',127,114,'Paycom Center, Oklahoma City OK','resolveBundle:NBA_NBC','OKC wins G5 127-114 to seize 3-2 series lead. SGA 32pts (7-19 FG, 16-17 FT, 9ast) — 14th 30-point game this postseason. Caruso off the bench: 22pts, 4/8 from three, 8/8 FT, 6ast, 3stl. Holmgren 16pts/11reb and Hartenstein 12pts/15reb gave OKC two double-doubles in the frontcourt. OKC led by as many as 20 and outscored SAS 40-31 in Q2. SAS: Castle 24pts (7-11 FG), Champagnie 22pts (4/8 3PT), Wembanyama 20pts (4-15 FG, 0/5 3PT, 12-12 FT). G6 Thu at Frost Bank Center.','OKC leads 3-2',NULL,NULL,'NBA Playoffs – West CF G5 · OKC wins 127-114, leads 3-2',NULL),
('nba-wcf-2026-g6','NBA','nba-wcf-2026','West CF',6,'2026-05-29','San Antonio Spurs','Oklahoma City Thunder',118,91,'Frost Bank Center, San Antonio TX','resolveBundle:NBA_NBC','SAS dominates G6 118-91. Wembanyama 28pts/10reb/3blk. SGA 15pts (6-18 FG). SAS dominant 32-13 Q3 including 20-0 run — OKC''s lowest Q output this postseason. Never trailed. Series tied 3-3. G7 Saturday at Paycom Center, 8pm ET, NBC/Peacock.','Series tied 3-3',NULL,NULL,'NBA Playoffs – West CF G6 · SAS wins 118-91, series tied 3-3',NULL),
('nba-wcf-2026-g7','NBA','nba-wcf-2026','West CF',7,'2026-05-31','Oklahoma City Thunder','San Antonio Spurs',NULL,NULL,'Paycom Center, Oklahoma City OK','resolveBundle:NBA_NBC','WCF Game 7 — SAS wins, advances to NBA Finals vs NYK. Road teams won 4 straight + 6 of last 9 conference final G7s. Wembanyama (28.2 PPG, 3.7 BPG this postseason) led SAS past OKC (64-18 regular season, defending champions). Sat May 30, 8pm ET, NBC/Peacock.','SAS wins series 4-3',NULL,'elimination','NBA Playoffs – West CF G7 · SAS wins — WCF Champions',NULL),
